Packages 
Package Description
graph
Provides a framework to use undirected graphs and to store a sequence of nodes belonging to the graph, i.e., a path.
parsing
package which contain a class responsible to parse a xml file containing information about a graph and simulation parameters.
pec
Provides a framework to use a pending event container which is a Priority Queue of events, ordered by their trigger instants.
simulation
provides a simulator that contains a pending event container and contains the main class that runs the simulator.
utilities
package that contains a class with auxiliar methods.
